{"tid":753990,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"亂噏出事！陸永講錯嘢刺中工藤佑采痛處","createTime":"2018-07-24T05:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T10:59:48.000Z","uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":148,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"273126011ebf59a4a30e199be28810c57bef16b6","tid":753990,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T05:08:38.000Z","msg":"今屆香港小姐的二十位侯選佳麗有份現身《big big channel大公司周年慶》，佳麗未曾踏足選美的台板，便有機會在大型活動上演出，讓她們初嘗大騷滋味，可謂相當懂得善用資源。她們在王浩信獻唱劇集《不懂撒嬌的女人》插曲《陪着你走》時在旁伴舞，眾人表現淡定。之後大會司儀即場訪問佳麗，考驗她們的口才，其中陸永問到港日混血兒工藤佑采會否向爸爸請教日文，她表示爸爸已經去世多年，認真開口夾著脷，氣氛尷尬。"},{"pid":"bf544e5c90a2ded10510f17f7686c63932c651fe","tid":753990,"uid":19979,"like":490,"dislike":5,"score":485,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T05:12:18.000Z","msg":"條問題好正常姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ac0482fa0ffff1b32b833df8ba4c4ccb7a07ce","tid":753990,"uid":118011,"like":343,"dislike":5,"score":338,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T05:13:44.000Z","msg":"咁洗唔洗每次問每個港姐野之前都查左家宅先"},{"pid":"6ce498ece2e48eb9c270116a4d59fa070c50195c","tid":753990,"uid":51720,"like":100,"dislike":1,"score":99,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T05:18:19.000Z","msg":"好有台灣新聞Feel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd690c65f65498a466c7b462791f92f61dc68424","tid":753990,"uid":37005,"like":135,"dislike":2,"score":133,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T05:35:32.000Z","msg":"個問題都唔算亂噏姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f9ef81b264112d4ca9ed9d149856ad7fef4a2e1","tid":753990,"uid":57035,"like":161,"dislike":4,"score":157,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T05:46:37.000Z","msg":"鬼估到你真係死唒老豆老母咩"},{"pid":"a2caeb1aa4a2d08e6b19a00bb07a126ea1b2c408","tid":753990,"uid":146604,"like":10,"dislike":59,"score":-49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T05:54:25.000Z","msg":"唔做功課學人做主持"},{"pid":"c34376f9147a4f9791430dba456f03b831e910e2","tid":753990,"uid":150014,"like":10,"dislike":114,"score":-104,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2